I used to use shortwave radios in the 70&#39;s (my dad had a small
collection) to try to tune in other wordly beings. I guess today
people would refer to the entities I was trying to reach as ethereals.
I believed then as I do now the non-physical beings are all around us.
  The possibility sparked my imagination but I wasn&#39;t quite sure what
I was doing, I even used to speak to my radio even though there was no
mic as I suspected I could connect psychically. -Bill

